Use axin-personal-ip-illustrations/SKILL.md as the source of truth.

This repo packages a multi-platform personal IP illustration workflow for Codex, Hermes, Claude Code, Cursor, Windsurf, Cline, OpenCode, and generic agents.

Default visual rules:
- 16:9 Chinese article illustration.
- Pure white background.
- Minimal black hand-drawn line art.
- Sparse red/orange/blue handwritten notes.
- Large white space.
- Character performs the core conceptual action.

Use 阿鑫 / Axin as the default and only recurring character: a hand-drawn human with black hair, round glasses, and a hoodie.

Run scripts/validate-repo.ps1 before committing.
